==Japanese==
===Phrase===
'''[[良い]]お[[年]]をお[[迎える|迎え]]下さい''' (よいおとしをおむかえください, ''yoi otoshi wo omukae kudasai'')
# (''formal'') [I, we] wish you a happy new year (''litt.''‘meet a good year’) (NB this Japanese expression should be used before the old year expires, but is rarely used among close friends)
===Phrase===
'''良いお年を''' (よいおとしを, ''yoi otosi wo'')
# (shorter, less formal form of [[良いお年をお迎え下さい]])
